{"tid":2099951,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲擬向港人提供「天安門式」簽證","createTime":"2020-07-08T15:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T02:04:11.000Z","uid":331319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"177b16dee518d9203491aedaa9aae97e850bc516","tid":2099951,"uid":331319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據報澳洲擬向港人提供「天安門式」簽證<br />\n「港版國安法」生效之後，隨即引來國際社會關注，有國家向港人提供援助。據澳洲媒體報道，澳洲將予在當地的港人提供「天安門式」簽證（Tiananmen-style visas）。<br />\n據報澳洲總理莫理森會於當地周三（7月8日）晚上，向內閣提出建議，最快會在周四或周五公布措施。<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-08-2020%2F64301&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=28cdc259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64301</a>"},{"pid":"6566e8fbd6f070402b905ee5c898e503be751d40","tid":2099951,"uid":245831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"啫係乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa42a425eaac0ad8b519e2e4f5b2270b7b361d28","tid":2099951,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94cef819df3389a167a670a0632c70d2a2ec70d","tid":2099951,"uid":361247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"177b16dee518d9203491aedaa9aae97e850bc516","tid":2099951,"uid":331319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據報澳洲擬向港人提供「天安門式」簽證<br />\n「港版國安法」生效之後，隨即引來國際社會關注，有國家向港人提供援助。據澳洲媒體報道，澳洲將予在當地的港人提供「天安門式」簽證（Tiananmen-style visas）。<br />\n據報澳洲總理莫理森會於當地周三（7月8日）晚上，向內閣提出建議，最快會在周四或周五公布措施。<br 